\begin{document}
${V_{{{\mathrm{H}}_{\mathrm{2}}}{\mathrm{O}}}}$\end{document} value, suggesting that Zn atoms effectively lock H2O molecules in place. As Cu content increases, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
